&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;629&quot; data-end=&quot;1050&quot;&gt;We‚Äôre looking for a &lt;strong data-start=&quot;649&quot; data-end=&quot;687&quot;&gt;(Senior) Technical Product Manager&lt;/strong&gt; to shape the future of automation and intent detection in a world increasingly powered by AI. In this role, you‚Äôll own the product lifecycle‚Äîfrom identifying evolving threats and researching new detection techniques, to delivering products that help customers classify traffic, protect digital experiences, and integrate detection insights into security systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1052&quot; data-end=&quot;1241&quot;&gt;You‚Äôll work alongside a globally distributed team of engineers, data scientists, and fraud experts. We move fast, value deep curiosity, and create space for individual ownership and impact.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;hr class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1243&quot; data-end=&quot;1246&quot;&gt;
&lt;h3 class=&quot;&quot; data-start=&quot;1248&quot; data-end=&quot;1273&quot;&gt;üîç &lt;strong data-start=&quot;1255&quot; data-end=&quot;1273&quot;&gt;What You‚Äôll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
